%F A001108 a(n) = floor(sqrt(2*A001110(n))) = floor(A001109(n)*sqrt(2)) = 2*(A000129(n)^2) - (n mod 2) = A001333(n)^2 - 1 + (n mod 2). - _Henry Bottomley_, Apr 19 2000, corrected by _Eric Rowland_, Jun 23 2017
